headline: Prudential Financial Elects Joseph Wolk to Board of Directors
summary: NEWARK, N.J., September 30, 2025--Prudential Financial, Inc. (NYSE: PRU) announced today that Joseph Wolk has been elected to the Board of Directors as an independent director.
